      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NEEDS SPACE (1) boasts a consistent overall record including nine wins from 22 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when third (30.86) over 530m at this track. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. PAW EVA (2) had been going along well winning a Grade 5 three back then placing at Gawler before missing the frame latest when seventh (31.17) at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. PRINCESS TILLEY (7) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (19.39) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Bold showing expected. STORMY DAY (5) justified the favourite's tag last time - sure to feature again.",
